      <title>经济强劲推动安大略省选举前收入增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stronger-economy-boosts-ontario-revenue-ahead-of-possible-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安大略省在一份经济更新报告中表示，税收驱动的收入增加将缓解安大略省的预算赤字，为政府在明年春季潜在选举之前提供支出空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stronger-economy-boosts-ontario-revenue-ahead-of-possible-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 17:28:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>锂业困境导致中国主要生产商今年迄今亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/lithium-woes-leave-top-china-producers-with-year-to-date-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于电池金属市场低迷持续挤压该行业，中国两大锂生产商今年前九个月仍处于亏损状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/lithium-woes-leave-top-china-producers-with-year-to-date-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 17:24:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管存在危险信号，Polymarket 对华尔街选举“游戏计划”的影响力仍在不断增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们普遍怀疑投资者应该在多大程度上相信加密货币预测市场 Polymarket 发出的信号，但华尔街仍密切关注该平台上的押注，该平台显示唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选的可能性很高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:16:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯的“一品脱啤酒便宜货”未能取悦英国酒吧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-pub-shares-rise-after-alcohol-duty-cut-on-pints-of-beer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管英国工党政府试图通过降低啤酒价格来赢得支持，但英国的酒吧和餐馆仍抱怨税收和工资成本上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-pub-shares-rise-after-alcohol-duty-cut-on-pints-of-beer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:16:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在强烈抗议下不再进一步提高石油和天然气税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-goes-no-further-in-raising-north-sea-tax-amid-industry-outcry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府并未进一步收紧针对北海石油和天然气生产商的税收制度，而是采取已经宣布的措施，在业界抗议之后，保留了暴利税中的资本津贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-goes-no-further-in-raising-north-sea-tax-amid-industry-outcry</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:11:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国债券下跌，因为里夫斯的预算指向更多债务和刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-adds-19-billion-in-bond-sales-to-fund-labour-s-fiscal-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国债券价格下跌，因为投资者对政府的投资融资和刺激经济的计划感到不安，这可能意味着利率将在较长时间内维持在高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-adds-19-billion-in-bond-sales-to-fund-labour-s-fiscal-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:58:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权管理人面临英国 32% 的附带权益税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/private-equity-managers-to-pay-32-tax-on-uk-carry-from-april</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 表示，从 4 月份开始，在英国买卖公司的私募股权经理将需要就其所得利润缴纳 32% 的税，这一举措对收购行业的增税幅度并没有一些人担心的那么高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/private-equity-managers-to-pay-32-tax-on-uk-carry-from-april</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:35:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济停滞，德国能源需求将创历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/german-energy-demand-set-to-hit-new-record-low-as-economy-stagnates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[研究机构 AG Energiebilanzen 称，由于欧洲最大经济体增长停滞，德国能源消耗量将连续第二年降至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/german-energy-demand-set-to-hit-new-record-low-as-economy-stagnates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 12:22:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
